849
01:25:23,535 --> 01:25:25,285
Timmy.

850
01:25:53,731 --> 01:25:55,524
Kérlek, ne!

851
01:25:56,943 --> 01:26:00,696
Timmy, ne!

852
01:26:00,864 --> 01:26:02,823
